&quot;What's the difference between...?&quot; &quot;How to properly invest in the stock market?&quot; &quot;How do I become a future doctor like you, po?&quot; Share fun facts and hidden rules that only experts &amp; professionals know, and get a chance to win an Iphone 12, IPad 8 and Airpods!

[Campaign Duration]
Jul 25, 2021, 12:00 AM - Aug 7, 2021, 11:59PM 2021
[Campaign Mechanics]
1. The campaign is open to anyone from the Philippines; 
2. Entrant must upload at least three (3) videos on TikTok within the campaign duration (Jul 25, 2021, 12:00 AM - Aug 7, 2021, 11:59PM 2021). You can upload as many video entries as you like; 
3. Only related educational and instructive videos with the hashtag #onlyexpertknows and #EDUSGOTTALENT2021 will be eligible; 
4. All videos should be original and follow TikTok's Community Guidelines; 
5. All videos need to be vertical screen and above 15 seconds; 
6. The winners will be selected ranking by the total number of &quot;Likes&quot; of your Top 3 most liked videos; 
7. 1st prize will be Apple Iphone 12, 2nd-3th prize will be iPad 8th Gen, 4th-5th prize will be Apple Airpods 2 and 6th-20th will be exclusive TikTok merch box； 
8. Winners will be announced on Aug 13, 2021 at 4PM through the in-app push notification and H5 in-app page. We will contact you via @tiktokphilippines official account to collect the delivery address and deliver the prizes to you within 30 days.

